# Project core

Personal static site: **Astro 7 + Svelte 5 islands → GitHub Pages**. No app server. Tools run in the browser.

## Read first

- `SYSTEM_ARCHITECTURE.md` — architecture, deploy, customization
- `package.json` — scripts
- `astro.config.ts` — `site`, `base`, static output, redirects
- `.github/copilot-instructions.md` — contributor conventions

## Hard constraints

- Keep `output: 'static'`. Do not introduce SSR/API backends unless the user explicitly changes hosting.
- Always use `import.meta.env.BASE_URL` (or `BASE`) for internal links/assets (PR previews set `ASTRO_BASE`).
- `trailingSlash: 'always'`. Preserve blog URLs: `/blog/YYYY/MM/DD/slug.html`.
- Do not edit `dist/`, `test-results/`, `node_modules/`, or hand-edit `gh-pages`.
- Prefer minimal diffs; no drive-by refactors or unsolicited markdown docs.
- Match existing Bootstrap 5 + Font Awesome + dark layout patterns.

## Validation order (after meaningful changes)

1. `NODE_ENV=development npm run build`
2. `npm test`
3. `npm run check` (note: may already fail on main for `PostLayout` ogImage typing)
4. `npm run test:e2e` when UI/browser behavior changes

## Path aliases

`@layouts` `@components` `@data` `@utils` `@images` `@content` `@scripts` `@styles`

## Security / governance (always-on companions)

Also active: `security-anti-patterns.mdc`, `agent-governance.mdc`.  
Do not weaken them. Selective distillation of [sec-context](https://github.com/Arcanum-Sec/sec-context) + OWASP AI secure coding — not the full 65K-token dump.
